HEADWORD: Flagstone
<hw>Flag"stone`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A flat stone used
in paving, or any rock which will split into such stones. See
<er>Flag</er>, a stone.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

